    "text": [
        "Dear Mr Sharma,",
        "I would like to draw your attention to the mistake which take place in our company magazine article which was published by Times of India on 31st December 2021. This article was about our company future plans in which they wrote it company won\u2019t have a plan to expand our business in the energy sector while our primary focus is only in this sector.",
        "Let me explain in more detail, article says that our Ajanta Group are focusing on consumer product business only and the company won't see any future in the energy industry because of that our investor dumping off our companies shares.",
        "I would like to request you kindly contact the magazine company and tell them to correct the information. So, our investors can relax and stay with our organization. It would help our partners to connect with us. Moreover, it is a matter of prestige for our group.",
        "Kindly contact them so they can correct the information as soon as possible.",
        "Yours sincerely,",
        "Piyush Agarwal"
    ],
